      "text": "初めてなんだから仕方ないよ\nそれよりボールが速くて驚いたな。いい肩をしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ it’s your first time.\nBut I’m surprised by how fast the ball was. You have a good arm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8333306631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
