      "text": "基準が高過ぎないか……？\nでも安心したよ。後はコントロールだけだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t your standard too high…?\nBut I’m relieved. The control is all you need now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.466665268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
