      "text": "そうですね。さっきは力を抜き過ぎちゃって\nボールがすっぽ抜けちゃったみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. The ball went off my hand too early\nbecause I didn’t put enough force into it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8581173736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
