      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい！\n大丈夫ですか、コーチ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m sorry!\nAre you okay‚ Coach?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8376576739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.29999911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫……急所は外れてるから……\n今のは、ど真ん中だ。さくら、ナイスピッチ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m okay… It missed my vitals…\nThat was right down the middle. Sakura‚ nice pitch…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.29999911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2024196622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "コーチの顔が危険な色に……！？\nコーチ？　コーチーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Coach’s face is turning a dangerous color…?!\nCoach? Coach~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3024196622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5357529955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ふう、なんとか一命は取りとめたな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew‚ I barely survived…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6690934496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "酷い目に遭わせてしまって、本当にごめんなさい……\nこの後の練習は、私一人で大丈夫ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so sorry for almost killing you…\nI’ll be fine practicing on my own from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1453951618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.5951177595
    },
