      "text": "何言ってるんだ。最後まで付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? I’m staying until the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5951177595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……{user}さんに\nこれ以上怪我をさせちゃったら、私……",
